<dl id="n12006a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12006a">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12006a"> 6(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> at Noel go for a drink of water</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Sachez donc que la plupart d&apos;entr&apos;elles sortent pendant <mark>la nuit de No&euml;l</mark> de leur immobilit&eacute; s&eacute;culaire <mark>pour aller, par bandes, se d&eacute;salt&eacute;rer au ruisseau voisin</mark> <br><font color="green">[You should know that most of [the stones]</font> leave their age-old paralysis during Christmas night in order to go, in groups, to refresh themselves at the nearby stream] <small> l'Abb&eacute; A. Millon, <a name="AMPB" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#AMPB"><cite title="source">Pauvres Pierres! Les Megalithes Bretons devant la science</cite></a> (n.d) 19</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
